---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="HARDY - Pasta de maní ultra premium para atletas"
  description="Pasta de maní ultra premium para atletas exigentes. Ingredientes puros, calidad sin concesiones y rendimiento máximo."
>
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Background -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cream"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,rgba(195,33,54,0.10),transparent_55%)]"></div>
      
      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold text-neutral-900 leading-tight">
              Potenciá tu
              <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-400 to-accent-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                Rendimiento
              </span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
              Pasta de maní ultra premium para atletas que exigen lo mejor.
              Ingredientes puros, calidad sin concesiones y rendimiento máximo.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center">
            <a 
              href="/products" 
              class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500 to-accent-600 hover:from-accent-600 hover:to-accent-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl hover:shadow-accent-500/25 transform hover:scale-105"
            >
              Ver Colección Premium
            </a>
            <a 
              href="/about" 
              class="border-2 border-neutral-300 hover:border-accent-500 text-neutral-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-accent-50"
            >
              Nuestra Historia
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Stats -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-accent-400">30g</div>
              <div class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">Proteína por porción</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-accent-400">0</div>
              <div class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">Azúcares agregados</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-accent-400">100%</div>
              <div class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">Ingredientes naturales</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-accent-400">1M+</div>
              <div class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mt-1">Atletas nos eligen</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Scroll indicator -->
      <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-neutral-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Featured Products -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">
            Colección Premium
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-neutral-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Cada frasco está elaborado con los mejores ingredientes para impulsar tu entrenamiento
          </p>
        </div>
        
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Product 1 -->
            <div class="group bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 hover:ring-neutral-300 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.02]">
            <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-neutral-100 rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-400 to-accent-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-2xl">H</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Classic Power</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Maní tostado con un toque de sal marina. Ideal para antes de entrenar.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-400">$24.99</span>
              <button class="bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full transition-colors shadow-md">
                Agregar al carrito
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Product 2 -->
            <div class="group bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 hover:ring-neutral-300 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.02]">
            <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-neutral-100 rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-400 to-accent-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-2xl">H</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Protein Elite</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Potenciado con proteína vegetal. 35g de proteína por porción.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-400">$29.99</span>
              <button class="bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full transition-colors shadow-md">
                Agregar al carrito
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Product 3 -->
            <div class="group bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 hover:ring-neutral-300 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.02]">
            <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-neutral-100 rounded-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-400 to-accent-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-2xl">H</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Recovery Blend</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Con aceite MCT y hongos adaptógenos para una recuperación óptima.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-400">$34.99</span>
              <button class="bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full transition-colors shadow-md">
                Agregar al carrito
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Choose Us -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">
            La Diferencia HARDY
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-neutral-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            No solo hacemos pasta de maní. Creamos nutrición de alto rendimiento para atletas de élite.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center space-y-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-accent-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Ingredientes Premium</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-700">Solo el mejor maní, de origen responsable, llega a nuestros frascos.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center space-y-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-accent-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Enfoque en el Rendimiento</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-700">Formulado específicamente para atletas y fanáticos del fitness.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center space-y-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-accent-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Hecho con Pasión</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-700">Pequeños lotes elaborados con dedicación en nuestra planta de última generación.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-900 via-accent-800 to-accent-900">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-6">
          ¿Listo para elevar tu rendimiento?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-accent-100 mb-8">
          Sumate a miles de atletas que confían en HARDY para alcanzar sus metas.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/products" 
          class="inline-block bg-white hover:bg-neutral-100 text-accent-800 px-12 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-2xl"
        >
          Comprar ahora
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
</Layout>